results.name: Numerators of row sums of array of rationals A038566(n)/A020653(n), n>=2.
comment: See the W. Lang link under A038566 for the rationals and more.
formula: a(n)=numerator(sum(r(n, k), k=1..phi(n))), with phi(n)=A000010(n) (Euler's totient function) and r(n, k):=A038566(n,k)/A020653(n,k), n>=2, if A020653 is read as an irregular triangle.
results.author: _Wolfdieter Lang_, Sep 12 2005
